ing: 4 cups cooked long-grain white rice, cooled
1 (20 ounce) can DOLEÂ® Pineapple Chunks, drained
des: "This is a fun, fast and easy take on that traditional comfort food, rice pudding. The pineapple adds a sweet, irresistible zing."
ins:
Whisk together milk and pudding mix in large bowl, 2 to 3 minutes.
Stir in rice, pineapple chunks, raisins, cinnamon and vanilla.  Chill.
